data.description: This stunning freshly updated home boasts a seamless blend of modern polished design and cozy charm. Adorned with exquisite porcelain wood plank tile floors, every step resonates with warmth and sophistication. The expansive primary suite offers its own serene seclusion, not to mention separate double vanities, and oversized walk in shower. The spaciousness extends to the large kitchen, with gleaming stainless steel appliances, a captivating tile backsplash, and ample space to bring out your inner chef. Vaulted living room ceilings allow for an inviting ambiance perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing in comfort. As you step out to the newly screened in lanai, prepare to be enchanted by the fully fenced in backyard complete with panoramic views of the lush golf course, offering a picturesque backdrop for your everyday moments. Nestled in a St Augustine Shores, this residence is the embodiment of tranquility. Whether you’re savoring quiet moments indoors or enjoying the greenery and views outside, you’re sure to feel right at home. Come experience the epitome of St. Augustine living at 291 Cortez Drive — a place where comfort, elegance, and scenic beauty converge to create an extraordinary living experience. RECENT UPGRADES: Roof (2023), Dishwasher (2023), Garbage Disposal (2023), Gutters (2023), Exterior Paint (2023), Interior Paint (2023), Front Wooden Fence (2023), and HVAC (2022). Additional Interior Photos & Virtual Tour Coming Soon.
